      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed manual gearbox. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. Proactive maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the longevity of the crankshaft journals. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a functional M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque vectoring. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the subframe and VANOS system remain in excellent working order, providing the tactile hydraulic steering feedback and linear power delivery purists demand.",
